aju jul te saq mármol. Kub´ tna´n qa a Dobby b´a´n tu´n t-xi t-k´amo´n jun tb´anil muqb´il,
extzen tzalu a elf n-chi kub´ ten kyxol tze´ toj jun jul b´incha´n nya b´a´n. N-ximane qa
