extzen tej ky-ka´yin kykyaqil xjal ti´j, xi tq´ama´n te elf kyimni t-xe´
te muqb´il. “Nimxix chjonte teya Dobby tu´n tzaj ttzaqpi´na weye toj tkub´el a´. Aju
mya b´a´nxix extzen il ti´j tu´n t-kyime tej t-xi´ya b´a´n extzen tzaj t-xob´a. kukx chin b´ete
na'ntza aju tbinchaya ki'je. In chin ayone tiʼja tuʼn ttzalaja jaʼlo».
