najchaq ti´j t-karsel tjaq´ tx´otx´; pero aju xjel ti tten
ex tej t-xi kykuʼtz chej kukxtoq in che xobʼ. Myia b´i´n t-xim
jte´ amb´il n-chi b´et ky-b´et aye dragón mya n-chi kub´ tz´aq, extzen jte´ amb´il n-chi b´ant ky-b´et aye dragón lu,
aju noq ch´in n-ku tka´yin, n-chi kanet jun tb´anil najb´il tun t-xi tq´o´n. Xi tka´yin
ttxlaj tkyaqil maj, n-ximana qa n-ku tna´n t-xu´k n-chi tzaj t-xob´il.
