n-chi b´et, n-chi tzalaj. A ttzmal twi´ mas nim twitz Harry
ma ku k'ayin. Kubʼ tyekʼin tibʼ ex bʼaj t-xiten. Mas matij ex mas matij e chʼiy kabʼe tilbʼilal, tzmaxi tej
noq o´kx ky-wi´ extzen ky-xu´k n-chi noj ti´j tilb´ilal. Yajxitl tkyaqil tzaj t-xob´il
twitz muro ik tza´n jun tal ttzi ja, extzen aju ttzi ja te jun axix tok tunel
ma txi tnam. extzen aye q-xol, t-xmakal t-xmakal, t-xmakal t-xmakal, t-xb´alin t-xmakal, tzaj t-xo´n tib´aj axix tok Neville Longbottom, aye tzaj tq´o´n jun tq´ajq´ajel twi´ tzalajb´il, tzaj t-xo´n tib´aj
a mantelpiece extzen tzaj tq´ajq´ajel twi´. ¡b´i´n wune qa tzula! b´i´n wune, Harry!
