aju in tzaj tqʼamaʼn qa at junjun kyxmilal mintiʼ kyipumal in che kubʼ kychʼixpuʼn kyqan twitz txʼotxʼ, aju in che bʼaj t-sbʼuʼn qe tqan tzeʼ
tx´otx´ n-chi yek´unte t-xe´chil k´ul. Xi t-jaqo´n twitz extzen xi tka´yin
tijxe.
